title: Week 8 Recap 2022
description:
Field Yates and Liz Loza recap everything you need to know from Week 8 of the NFL season where fantasy many stars delivered in a big way. Plus, Liz is joined by Eric Moody give an audio exclusive reaction to SNF including a strange game from Aaron Rodgers.
